{"tid":2029782,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)Why did you say that name!?","createTime":"2020-05-22T11:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T20:23:55.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cd1d9a5456bea9b3581ca5c2cc0b6f6df1567052","tid":2029782,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:53:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSg9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=704ceeb4\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSg9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=e673a32d\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSg9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=8b48b8b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/0ed12c08e37a66f2869366a6f5024496/tenor.gif?itemid=11777417\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2F0ed12c08e37a66f2869366a6f5024496%2Ftenor.gif%3Fitemid%3D11777417&h=a9cf6f46&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xSysuKP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FxSysuKP.jpg&h=30d3b613&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/54/6d/8d/546d8decbb6799b4372b18e0520c645a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F54%2F6d%2F8d%2F546d8decbb6799b4372b18e0520c645a.gif&h=7c5a1695&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.若干年前，奧林匹斯十二眾神之王宙斯創造出人類，但他的兒子戰神阿瑞斯因為妒忌而開始縱使人類發動戰爭，最後遭宙斯等眾神放逐至人間。臨終的宙斯創造出以保衛人類為使命的女戰士族「亞馬遜人」，集體居住在一座與世隔絕的天堂島，島上還遺留唯一能夠殺死阿瑞斯的利劍「弒神者」（Godkiller）。亞馬遜公主黛安娜從小嚮往著成為偉大的戰士，由於母親希波呂忒女王一直反對她習武，她只好偷偷和她的阿姨安提奧佩習武多年，雖然希波呂忒之後發現小孩瞞著她習武後，但也決定放棄阻止<br />\n<br />\n2.氪星是自然環境惡劣的遙遠行星，星球居民幾萬年來榨乾天然資源，導致星球核心開始不穩定。科學家喬&middot;艾爾試圖說服政府長老，讓他得到控制氪星人工生育的「中樞寶典」（Genetics Codex）來保證種族延續，但軍事領袖薩德將軍無法忍受墨守陳規而在這時發動政變。喬偷走寶典後與妻子蘿拉決定忍痛將他們剛出世的兒子凱&middot;艾爾送離氪星，將寶典輸進凱的基因裡保管，隨即將凱送進曲速太空艙中送至地球。絕望的薩德親手殺死喬，而政府軍成功奪回局勢抓獲薩德，將他與剩餘叛軍集體以冷凍狀態由監獄艦船送進幻影區中流放。不久，氪星氣數已盡，蘿拉許願希望兒子凱「創造一個更好的世界」後與星球陪葬。凱的船迫降在美國堪薩斯州齊莫維爾小鎮的一塊農田，被農夫夫婦強納森和瑪莎&middot;肯特收養，起名「克拉克&middot;肯特」<br />\n<br />\n3.由超人和薩德將軍的恩怨所引發的「黑零事件」過了十八個月，超人成為了一個備受爭議的英雄人物，處於被支持者和反對者之間共同擠壓。與此同時，億萬富翁布魯斯&middot;韋恩已經化身為黑暗騎士「蝙蝠俠」，守護了高譚市接近二十年，而他因為在事件裏損失了位於大都會的韋恩企業分部與多名好友，開始將超人視為潛在威脅。而身為超人的克拉克&middot;肯特得知蝙蝠俠近年來的「暴力執法」...<br />\n<br />\n4.數千年前，荒原狼和他的外星生物軍團天啟魔，妄圖利用三個母盒之統一力量來摧毀地球生態系統，再將其改造成為荒原狼家鄉的蒼夷景象。他的邪惡計畫最終被奧林匹斯十二眾神、亞馬遜人、亞特蘭提斯人、人類以及綠光軍團攜手合作奮戰而挫敗，荒原狼被迫撤離地球，三個分離的母盒分別被亞馬遜人、亞特蘭提斯人和人類回收保管，分開藏於地球各個隱秘角落好永不被人找到。於現代，全世界還沒走出超人之死的陰影，高譚市和大都會等城市的犯罪率急劇上升，景象不但造成三個母盒自行重啟，甚至讓荒原狼重新現身於地球，決定再次實施征服計畫好博得他的君主達克賽德<br />\n<br />\n8 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSg9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=959da3b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSg9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=23a4d905\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c8b014e7e433b39f57182c7afbf92954cfc3d8f","tid":2029782,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mj8GKsB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmj8GKsB.gif&h=1a7dfcdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u9cwneg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu9cwneg.jpg&h=30bf2e35&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88799f89a593eda19712c5086da5db2e33f5c642","tid":2029782,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:11:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45de754e8471844b184e29b3f8ef84720367952b","tid":2029782,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e8c2e43c97ba0a80af83b3350379fdda788d25","tid":2029782,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2473f8f58c5c4b46eb204b64c6f70cdbbaa295c","tid":